Question Text: Include in NORC Incentive Eligibility List
Variable Label: Include in NORC Incentive Eligibility List
Notes: If SMInct_IncentiveCat_v1r0 is 1 and RcrtES_Site_v1r0 is 8 then 0; if SMInct_IncentiveCat_v1r0 is 1 and RcrtES_Site_v1r0 ne 8 then 1
Derivation Notes: This variable is needed to exclude UChicago participants from NORC's incentive list
